  <constraints>
    <constraint source="ADR-021">Fluent v9 + Griffel `makeStyles` + semantic tokens mandatory. Column tints MUST use semantic tokens (e.g. tokens.colorPaletteRedBackground1 / tokens.colorPaletteYellowBackground1 / tokens.colorPaletteGreenBackground1 or equivalent). NO hex literals. Verify exact token names available in @fluentui/react-components.</constraint>
    <constraint source="ADR-012">Reuse shared lib primitives where possible: Fluent v9 Button, Input, ToggleButton</constraint>
    <constraint source="UAT 2">Open is always-enabled regardless of selection. When 0 selected, dispatch openTodo with NO todoId — Code Page lands on its default view. When 1+ selected, dispatch with first todoId — modal opens that record.</constraint>
    <constraint source="UAT 7">Quick-add creates ONLY the title field on sprk_todo. Other required fields (statecode, statuscode) use Dataverse defaults. If Dataverse rejects the create due to missing required fields, surface a graceful error + offer to "Open full wizard" link.</constraint>
    <constraint source="durable user instruction">spaarkedev1 deploys are master-only; do NOT propose a branch deploy</constraint>
  </constraints>

