  <context>
    <background>
      Wave D's R4-099 made the widget's toolbar `[SearchBox, +, Open, refresh]`. UAT 2026-06-18 changed direction: search should be an ICON (less visual weight by default), Open should be ALWAYS-ON (parity with app's behavior — let user "just open the app" regardless of selection), column cards need visual differentiation, and quick-add inline is a new feature for fast capture without the wizard friction.
    </background>
